        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">cobas e 801 thyroid-stimulating hormone (TSH) assay reported false positive results (&gt;10 mIU/L) in 12 euthyroid patients due to biotin interference.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">INC-011</rdfs:label>
    </owl:NamedIndividual>
    


